1. Decide if you would like pizza for dinner
2. Decide which business to order from
3. Decide which type of pizza to order (Thin crust, stuffed crust, deep dish)
4. Decide what toppings you would like (pepperoni, olives, peppers, extra cheese, sausage, pineapple)
5. Decide if you would like sides or drinks with your order.
6. Decide if you want to pick the pizza up or have it delivered.
7. Call the business and place the order.
8. Drive to the business to pick up the pizza, or leave a tip for the delivery driver.
9. Eat the entire pizza in one sitting.